  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Steamed Twigs</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Steamed Twigs</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">food</a> added to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>. It can be eaten by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo\" title=\"Beefalo\">Beefalo</a> but not by players, and is classified as Roughage. It requires one of <i>any</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedible\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Inedible\">Inedible</a> ingredient (other than <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Fuel\" title=\"Nightmare Fuel\">Nightmare Fuel</a>), and does not accept <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats/DST\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats/DST\">Meat</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\">Fish</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Food\" title=\"Monster Food\">Monster Food</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy\" title=\"Dairy\">Dairy</a>, or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Magic_Value\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magic Value\">Magic</a> ingredients. The simplest recipe uses four <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a>, but <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruits\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fruits\">Fruits</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vegetables\">Vegetables</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a> can also be used as the filler.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedible\" title=\"Inedible\"><img alt=\"Inedible.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Inedible.png?5e8ada\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>filler cannot be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\">Fishes</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Food\" title=\"Monster Food\">Monster Food</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy\" title=\"Dairy\">Dairy</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Magic_Value\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magic Value\">Magic Value</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Potato\" title=\"Potato\"><img alt=\"Potato.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Potato.png?cac9b1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Cap\" title=\"Red Cap\"><img alt=\"Red Cap.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Cap.png?468bf1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berries\" title=\"Berries\"><img alt=\"Berries.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berries.png?629a2e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Cap\" title=\"Red Cap\"><img alt=\"Red Cap.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Cap.png?468bf1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Forget-Me-Lots.png?be6524\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Forget-Me-Lots.png?be6524\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Dried Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Dried Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dried_Forget-Me-Lots.png?332337\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Forget-Me-Lots\">Forget-Me-Lots</a> can be farmed with the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lord_of_the_Fruit_Flies\" title=\"Lord of the Fruit Flies\">Lord of the Fruit Flies</a>, then used as filler to preserve Twigs, or cooked with a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Birchnut\" title=\"Birchnut\">Birchnut</a> to make <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beefalo_Treats\" title=\"Beefalo Treats\">Beefalo Treats</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nutribrick\" title=\"Nutribrick\"><img alt=\"Nutribrick.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nutribrick.png?b1c9fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nutribrick\" title=\"Nutribrick\"><img alt=\"Nutribrick.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nutribrick.png?b1c9fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nutribrick\" title=\"Nutribrick\"><img alt=\"Nutribrick.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nutribrick.png?b1c9fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nutribrick\" title=\"Nutribrick\"><img alt=\"Nutribrick.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nutribrick.png?b1c9fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Other <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedibles\" title=\"Inedibles\">Inedibles</a> (other than <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Fuel\" title=\"Nightmare Fuel\">Nightmare Fuel</a>) will also result in Steamed Twigs.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nutribrick\" title=\"Nutribrick\"><img alt=\"Nutribrick.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nutribrick.png?b1c9fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Volt_Goat_Horn\" title=\"Volt Goat Horn\"><img alt=\"Volt Goat Horn.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Volt_Goat_Horn.png?8795d0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bone_Shards\" title=\"Bone Shards\"><img alt=\"Bone Shards.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bone_Shards.png?291c61\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Any combination of Inedibles (with or without <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruits\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fruits\">Fruits</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vegetables\">Vegetables</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a> as fillers) will make Steamed Twigs.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nutribrick\" title=\"Nutribrick\"><img alt=\"Nutribrick.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nutribrick.png?b1c9fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Forget-Me-Lots.png?be6524\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Forget-Me-Lots.png?be6524\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Forget-Me-Lots\" title=\"Dried Forget-Me-Lots\"><img alt=\"Dried Forget-Me-Lots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dried_Forget-Me-Lots.png?332337\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs\" title=\"Steamed Twigs\"><img alt=\"Steamed Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Twigs.png?87ba15\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tips\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/32px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Tips</span></h2>\n<ul><li>If the player wants to cook <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wet_Goop\" title=\"Wet Goop\">Wet Goop</a> instead, which is used to craft the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Terra_Firma_Tamper\" title=\"Terra Firma Tamper\">Terra Firma Tamper</a>, they can do this by cooking three Twigs and a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meat</a>, an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Egg</a>, a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy\" title=\"Dairy\">Dairy food</a> or a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Fuel\" title=\"Nightmare Fuel\">Nightmare Fuel</a>. This is because those ingredients are excluded from the Steamed Twigs recipe.</li>\n<li>It is worth considering that beefalo get 4 times more health than what is listed. Steamed Twigs grant 2.66x the amount of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\">Hunger</a> that 4 twigs would give, and 7.5x the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\">Health</a>.</li></ul>\n<p><br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Twigs#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
