  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nSteamed Twigs\nFood Info\n100\n15\n0\nRoughage\nWood\n(non-survivor food)\nObject Info\n20 Days\n40\nCooking Info\nx1 x3\n10 sec\n-5\nMiscellaneous\n\"beefalofeed\"\n“None for me, thank you.”\n–Wilson\n“Alright smelly, eat up!”\n–Willow\n“Hair-cow, come! Wolfgang has food for you!”\n–Wolfgang\n“I wouldn't want my beefalo to starve.”\n–Wendy\n“COME EAT YOUR STICKS”\n–WX-78\n“Beefalo seem to be quite adept at digesting sticks.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Come and get it!”\n–Woodie\n“I suppose I'd better keep the stupid beast fed.”\n–Maxwell\n“I must keep my beast fed and battle-ready.”\n–Wigfrid\n“We take good care of our beefalo.”\n–Webber\n“My beast could use some more meat on its bones.”\n–Warly\n“Belly stuff for Shaggy Buddy”\n–Wormwood\n“Feedin' time!”\n–Winona\n“It really sticks to the ribs, hyuyu!”\n–Wortox\n“Big fuzzy! Have sticks for you!”\n–Wurt\n“Come here, beefalo! Dinner time!”\n–Walter\n“Did i remember to feed my beefalo today?”\n–Wanda\nSteamed Twigs is a Crock Pot food added to Don't Starve Together. It can be eaten by Beefalo but not by players, and is classified as Roughage. It requires one of any Inedible ingredient (other than Nightmare Fuel), and does not accept Meat, Fish, Monster Food, Eggs, Dairy, or Magic ingredients. The simplest recipe uses four Twigs, but Fruits, Vegetables, and Ice can also be used as the filler.\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×3\nfiller cannot be Meats, Fishes, Monster Food, Eggs, Dairy, and Magic Value.\nExamples[edit | edit source]\nForget-Me-Lots can be farmed with the Lord of the Fruit Flies, then used as filler to preserve Twigs, or cooked with a Birchnut to make Beefalo Treats.\nOther Inedibles (other than Nightmare Fuel) will also result in Steamed Twigs.\nAny combination of Inedibles (with or without Fruits, Vegetables or Ice as fillers) will make Steamed Twigs.\nTips[edit | edit source]\nIf the player wants to cook Wet Goop instead, which is used to craft the Terra Firma Tamper, they can do this by cooking three Twigs and a Meat, an Egg, a Dairy food or a Nightmare Fuel. This is because those ingredients are excluded from the Steamed Twigs recipe.\nIt is worth considering that beefalo get 4 times more health than what is listed. Steamed Twigs grant 2.66x the amount of Hunger that 4 twigs would give, and 7.5x the Health.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
