  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Cành Cây Hấp là một món ăn trong Nồi Hầm được thêm vào Don&#x27;t Starve Together. Nó có thể được ăn bởi Bò Lai nhưng người chơi thì không, và được phân loại là Thức ăn thô. Nó yêu cầu một trong bất kỳ thành phần Không ăn được nào (trừ Nhiên liệu Ác mộng) và không chấp nhận các thành phần Thịt, Cá, Thức ăn Quái vật, Trứng, Sữa hoặc Ma thuật. Công thức đơn giản nhất sử dụng bốn Cành cây, nhưng Trái cây, Rau và Đá cũng có thể được sử dụng làm chất độn.</p>",
  "title": "Steamed Twigs",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|image = Steamed Twigs Dropped.png\n|icon = Steamed Twigs.png\n|foodType = {{FoodType|Roughage|notext=1}}<br>{{FoodType|Wood}}\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32|Inedible}}x1 {{Pic|32|Filler}}x3\n|hpRestored     = 15\n|hungerRestored = 100\n|sanityRestored = 0\n|cooktime       = 10 sec\n|priority       = -5\n|spoil          = 20 Days\n|stack          = 40\n|spawnCode      = \"beefalofeed\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = None for me, thank you.\n|willow = Alright smelly, eat up!\n|wolfgang = Hair-cow, come! Wolfgang has food for you!\n|wendy = I wouldn't want my beefalo to starve.\n|wx78 = COME EAT YOUR STICKS\n|wickerbottom = Beefalo seem to be quite adept at digesting sticks.\n|woodie = Come and get it!\n|maxwell = I suppose I'd better keep the stupid beast fed.\n|wigfrid = I must keep my beast fed and battle-ready.\n|webber = We take good care of our beefalo.\n|warly = My beast could use some more meat on its bones.\n|wormwood = Belly stuff for Shaggy Buddy\n|winona = Feedin' time!\n|wortox = It really sticks to the ribs, hyuyu!\n|wurt = Big fuzzy! Have sticks for you!\n|walter = Come here, beefalo! Dinner time!\n|wanda = Did i remember to feed my beefalo today?}}\n'''Steamed Twigs''' is a [[Crock Pot]] [[food]] added to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]''. It can be eaten by [[Beefalo]] but not by players, and is classified as Roughage. It requires one of ''any'' [[Inedible]] ingredient (other than [[Nightmare Fuel]]), and does not accept [[Meats/DST|Meat]], [[Fishes|Fish]], [[Monster Food]], [[Eggs]], [[Dairy]], or [[Magic Value|Magic]] ingredients. The simplest recipe uses four [[Twigs]], but [[Fruits]], [[Vegetables]], and [[Ice]] can also be used as the filler.\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Inedible\n|item2 = Filler\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|note = filler cannot be [[Meats]], [[Fishes]], [[Monster Food]], [[Eggs]], [[Dairy]], and [[Magic Value]].\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Twigs\n|item3 = Twigs\n|item4 = Twigs}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Twigs\n|item3 = Twigs\n|item4 = Potato}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Twigs\n|item3 = Red Cap\n|item4 = Ice}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Berries\n|item3 = Red Cap\n|item4 = Ice}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Forget-Me-Lots\n|item3 = Forget-Me-Lots\n|item4 = Dried Forget-Me-Lots\n|note=[[Forget-Me-Lots]] can be farmed with the [[Lord of the Fruit Flies]], then used as filler to preserve Twigs, or cooked with a [[Birchnut]] to make [[Beefalo Treats]].}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Nutribrick\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Nutribrick\n|item3 = Nutribrick\n|item4 = Nutribrick\n|note=Other [[Inedibles]] (other than [[Nightmare Fuel]]) will also result in Steamed Twigs.}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Nutribrick\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Volt Goat Horn\n|item3 = Bone Shards\n|item4 = Twigs\n|note=Any combination of Inedibles (with or without [[Fruits]], [[Vegetables]] or [[Ice]] as fillers) will make Steamed Twigs.\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Nutribrick\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Twigs\n|item2 = Forget-Me-Lots\n|item3 = Forget-Me-Lots\n|item4 = Dried Forget-Me-Lots\n}}\n{{clear}}\n== {{Pic32|Prototype}} Tips ==\n* If the player wants to cook [[Wet Goop]] instead, which is used to craft the [[Terra Firma Tamper]], they can do this by cooking three Twigs and a [[Meats|Meat]], an [[Eggs|Egg]], a [[Dairy|Dairy food]] or a [[Nightmare Fuel]]. This is because those ingredients are excluded from the Steamed Twigs recipe.\n* It is worth considering that beefalo get 4 times more health than what is listed. Steamed Twigs grant 2.66x the amount of [[Hunger]] that 4 twigs would give, and 7.5x the [[Health]].\n\n\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n[[vi:Steamed Twigs]]"
